      "contract": "Treat each input bit as logic one when its voltage is above `vth`. The MSB selects the folded half of the transfer. When `vd4` is high, add the lower-bit weighted value above midscale. When `vd4` is low, subtract the lower-bit weighted value from midscale. The lower bits use binary weights `4`, `2`, and `1`, and the output is scaled by `vref/16`.",
